title: Energy Projects-Mayors Stimulus 2009
name: Energy Projects-Mayors Stimulus 2009
description: This data represents the count of energy projects by city for the 2009 Mayors Stimulus Report from the US Conference of Mayors. The data was calculated using a pivot table to find counts of total energy projects, sum of funding, and sum of jobs created for cities across the United States. Locations were then geocoded using batchgeocode.com and uploaded as a csv.
